                            <comment id="74926" author="utopiabound" created="Tue, 14 Jan 2014 14:39:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The number of files can&apos;t be decreased for this test, so it should be EXCEPTED until file create rate on ZFS can be brought up to par with ldiskfs.&lt;/p&gt;

